message.body: Hey Cary. Did u still wanna hang out tonight? I lost my debit card this weekend so I can't go anywhere but if u wanna come over that's cool. I thought maybe we could play a board game
What game were you thinking? Or we could go to quizzo though i guess i'd be paying :-)
I have trivial pursuit. Quizzo where? Yeah I have like $10 in cash on me
Tangiers or new deck or sidecar i think. Maybe not the most convenient..?
I only heard of new deck..by Penn right?
Yeah. Theirs is at ten and Tangiers is at nine on 18 and Lombard
You dunno of any in center city?
18 and Lombard is center city right?
Oh I kinda thought that was so Phila. OK that is best place for me then. I need a bike!
There is also north star bar at seven
Where's that?
Poplar and twenty seven. A little closer to you
Oooh apparently its legendary
OK u wanna go there?
Yeah i'm game. It's nice and early. I have some boring chores to do after
Lol chores eh? OK I'll leave here at 630 then
Remember this. It is the answer to the online question. Rene robert cavelier.
Yep. Chores. I'm going to la on wednesday. I could go a little early if you want
Well its saved in my texts. I am cooking right now. So I'll text you when I'm done and can leave

Ohok. Its raining slightly. Not too chilly tho lil windy
Nice. Much better than the morning

Mmm..I just didn't feel like it.
Yeah weather been crappy all day. Or gonna love that LA weather!
You're *
Haha yeah!
Heading over now

Here
Goodnight! Hope you made it home alright
